script#about-view-template(type="text/x-template")
  .view.about-view
    p.
      See #[a(href="https://foldingathome.org/") foldingathome.org] for
      information about the Folding@home project.

    p.
      Welcome to the Folding@home console.  This is the place to track your
      contributions to disease research and visualize what's happening on the
      Folding@home network.

    p.
      Many of the features of the console are still in development.  Here are
      some of the things will will be able to do in the future:

    ul
      li Monitor and control your clients.
      li Visualize proteins in 3D.
      li Earn social media points by promoting Folding@home.
      li Learn about the projects running on Folding@home.
      li Create new teams.
      li Edit team settings.
      li Monitor Work Server status.
      li Monitor your bonus status.
      li Change your Folding@home avatar.
